      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/copper-slides-to-three-week-low-on-fresh-jitters-over-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于市场对政府的促增长举措对需求究竟能有多大影响存疑，基本金属也跟随中国风险资产遭遇抛售。]]></description>
